<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200819/53219d98d5bb4ee9811df9efc071b507.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这次还是老套路，一前一后分开走。</p>
